464", "bbox": [803.4, 763.3, 871.1, 784.1]}, {"text": "$78.28", "bbox": [916.4, 763.3, 973.6, 784.1]}, {"text": "For the year ended December 31, 2017 and 2016, certain employees had restricted stock vesting and", "bbox": [225.0, 825.8, 1062.3, 846.6]}, {"text": "covered the aggregate statutory minimum tax withholding of $2.9 million and $3.1 million through a net", "bbox": [162.5, 850.8, 1034.9, 871.6]}, {"text": "settlement of 36,067 shares and 38,250 shares, respectively.", "bbox": [162.5, 875.8, 662.4, 896.6]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2017, there was $68.9 million of total unrecognized compensation cost related to", "bbox": [225.0, 925.8, 1073.4, 946.6]}, {"text": "nonvested share-based compensation arrangements granted under the 2013 Incentive Plan and the 2009 Incentive", "bbox": [162.5, 950.8, 1108.7, 971.6]}, {"text": "Plan. That cost is expected to be recognized over a weighted-average period of 2.53 years. As of December 31,", "bbox": [162.5, 975.8, 1089.5, 996.6]}, {"text": "2017, there were 2,911,770 and 604,331 nonvested stock options and restricted stock, respectively, of which", "bbox": [162.5, 1000.8, 1067.5, 1021.6]}, {"text": "2,450,191 and 509,701 are expected to vest. The total grant date fair value of options vested during the years", "bbox": [162.5, 1025.8, 1069.9, 1046.6]}, {"text": "ended December 31, 2017, 2016 and 2015 was $16.6 million, $14.2 million and $16.8 million, respectively. The", "bbox": [162.5, 1050.8, 1101.0, 1071.6]}, {"text": "total grant date fair value of restricted stock vested during the year ended December 31, 2017, 2016 and 2015", "bbox": [162.5, 1075.8, 1075.8, 1096.6]}, {"text": "was $17.6 million, $14.4 million and $16.3 million, respectively.", "bbox": [162.5, 1100.8, 704.8, 1121.6]}, {"text": "The Company also offers eligible employees the opportunity to participate in an employee stock purchase", "bbox": [225.0, 1150.8, 1108.3, 1171.6]}, {"text": "plan (“ESPP”). Under the ESPP, participating employees may authorize payroll deductions of up to 20.0% of", "bbox": [162.5, 1175.8, 1075.7, 1196.6]}, {"text": "their regular base salary and up to 50.0% of their short-term incentive compensation, both of which in total may", "bbox": [162.5, 1200.8, 1097.0, 1221.6]}, {"text": "not exceed twenty-five thousand dollars in any calendar year, to purchase shares of the Company’s common", "bbox": [162.5, 1225.8, 1066.5, 1246.6]}, {"text": "stock at a 5.0% discount of its fair market value at the time of purchase. In accordance with ASC 718, the ESPP", "bbox": [162.5, 1250.8, 1096.8, 1271.6]}, {"text": "is noncompensatory as the purchase discount is 5.0% or less from the fair market value, substantially all", "bbox": [162.5, 1275.8, 1032.2, 1296.6]}, {"text": "employees that meet limited employment qualifications may participate, and it incorporates no option features.", "bbox": [162.5, 1300.8, 1088.6, 1321.6]}, {"text": "During the years ended December 31, 2017, 2016 and 2015, the Company issued 29,605, 29,867 and 25,599", "bbox": [162.5, 1325.8, 1067.5, 1346.6]}, {"text": "shares of common stock at a weighted average discounted price of $81.38, $76.75 and $70.27, respectively.", "bbox": [162.5, 1350.8, 1060.9, 1371.6]}, {"text": "105", "bbox": [621.9, 1484.1, 653.1, 1504.9]}]}